# CODEOWNERS — who gets auto-requested for review on which paths.
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# As the community grows, reviewers add themselves next to the areas they steward.
# Until then, the core maintainers own everything. Replace @bee-ai-labs/maintainers with
# real handles/teams once the org is set up.

