/docs/security/         @bee-ai-labs/maintainers
/docs/deployment/       @bee-ai-labs/maintainers
/docs/mlops/            @bee-ai-labs/maintainers

# Runnable examples
/examples/              @bee-ai-labs/maintainers

# Repo infrastructure (higher bar for review)
